dc_title_s: Mykonos : 1:40 000. [Hodikoi chartes ton hellenikon neson] 103 = Mykonos 1:40 000. [Road maps of the Greek Islands] 103
dc_description_s: Alternate title: N. Mykonos= Is. Mykonos. Relief shown by 100 meter contour interval, gradient tints, and spot heights. "Me te Synergasia tes Geografikis Ypiresias Stratou = With the cooperation of the Hellenic Army Geographical Service." Ancillary Map: Mykonos = Mykonos (City map). Verso: Directory, tourist information, and Delos (archaeological site). Legend in Greek, English, German, and Italian; text in Greek and English. Map no.: 103. Tourist information on verso "103."
